de.saxsys.mvvmfx.utils.commands

Interface Command

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommandBase, CompositeCommand, DelegateCommand

    @Beta
public interface Command
    The Command encapsulates logic in the execute() method which will be called later. This can be used for example to provide an execute()-action which should perform on a button click.

    In addition it is possible to add the information on whether the Command can be executed at the moment or not (isExecutable()).

    Author:
    alexander.casall
